re":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:36:51.000Z","msg":"可能好多人第一次落工地，今日觀察到工友有啲位唔完美，可接受，要改善：<br />\n<br />\n- 北區人落雨有遮都唔鍾意開..下次自己唔用遮都可以遮下身邊有需要嘅人，守望相助<br />\n<br />\n-工友工作時要留意小心週圍手足；其他手足都小心碎片唔好行咁近，喺工地要有警覺性<br />\n<br />\n-封路手足set roadblock位同指揮交通都好重要，做唔到粗重嘢都仲有好多崗位，盡量唔好企喺度齋望<br />\n<br />\n今日真係好多人，估唔到💪🏻繼續努力繼續進步<br />\n&mdash;-From tg"},{"pid":"7e5ccf62b1bc4303fb6d2ceab28f2cdf3ee9b16c","tid":1622943,"uid":204207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:41:58.000Z","msg":"加油！早啲訓聽日見"},{"pid":"642ef8954c59849d37590fc0deff81b072203bfa","tid":1622943,"uid":262466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:42:07.000Z","msg":"反抗啊！！！"},{"pid":"af8e74cec1799e09854f7d2932377cdf1ee7c4ca","tid":1622943,"uid":184370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1e20d5b19e4d320a4dc951da87ba4a4bd185b0","tid":1622943,"uid":316717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:44:27.000Z","msg":"光復上水！"},{"pid":"cdcec8201bf691cdf53d501198057154f283c2a9","tid":1622943,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af8e74cec1799e09854f7d2932377cdf1ee7c4ca","tid":1622943,"uid":184370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4240f76353b6372d1b46caf1af86b91d9daab39a","tid":1622943,"uid":281543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:45:07.000Z","msg":"好多人連遮都冇帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee5ca336adc2408f515c1f081d480d3a9616bb94","tid":1622943,"uid":289900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:45:25.000Z","msg":"光復上水啊你老母<img src=