>\n好彩今日北區唔受尊重<br />\n唔係就好危險架<br />\n真係唔好再開路比車過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565705ccd12786742899512314fe18febb51e947","tid":1622943,"uid":271473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:47:28.000Z","msg":"北區幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8059c09d66887ce708d2ff6db6587d6d8ce193e1","tid":1622943,"uid":329675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:47:54.000Z","msg":"北區人<br />\n發夢見到有段時間D人好散<br />\n唔知係專登分散be water<br />\n定係真係唔知做咩<br />\n隊頭分散左<br />\n後面唔知要行去邊<br />\n另外求Tg<br />\n或者下次專登開個北區PO比人跟進最新動向？"},{"pid":"2799949b587c31ae8df18254828f7e33669aa88c","tid":1622943,"uid":204207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:48:07.000Z","msg":"搬鐵馬個啲同我帶手套"},{"pid":"0868a47752fc48390717cf5b7ade2ef0fb559a72","tid":1622943,"uid":184370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e9beea8aaf15d90fb58b0c961825a0ba4bab99","tid":1622943,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0868a47752fc48390717cf5b7ade2ef0fb559a72","tid":1622943,"uid":184370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hkqs0Zg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhkqs0Zg.png&h=f313513f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face